<section class="mushroom-benefits">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow" style="color:#5B414A;">Why It Works</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="color:#000;">Every sip working for you.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-grid">

      <!-- Focus -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon-wrap" style="background:#EEE8F4;">
          <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M9.5 2A4.5 4.5 0 0 0 5 6.5c0 1.4.64 2.66 1.65 3.5A3 3 0 0 0 5 12.5a3 3 0 0 0 2.05 2.84C7.28 16.87 8.52 18 10 18h4c1.48 0 2.72-1.13 2.95-2.66A3 3 0 0 0 19 12.5a3 3 0 0 0-1.65-2.68A4.5 4.5 0 0 0 14.5 2c-1.03 0-1.98.35-2.73.92A4.48 4.48 0 0 0 9.5 2z" fill="#6260AE"/>
            <path d="M12 9v9M9 12h6" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Focus</h3>
        <div class="benefit-dose">900mg Lion's Mane</div>
        <p>A nootropic mushroom studied for nerve growth factor production and cognitive clarity. Helps you think sharper, stay on task.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Energy -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon-wrap" style="background:#FEF0E7;">
          <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M13 2L4 13h7v9l9-11h-7V2z" fill="#F37024"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Energy</h3>
        <div class="benefit-dose">700mg Cordyceps</div>
        <p>Used by athletes for oxygen utilization and cellular energy production. Sustained energy — no caffeine, no crash.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Calm -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon-wrap" style="background:#EDF6E0;">
          <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 3C8 3 5 7 5 11c0 3.5 2 6.5 5 8v2h4v-2c3-1.5 5-4.5 5-8 0-4-3-8-7-8z" fill="#7FB540"/>
            <path d="M12 11v8" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path d="M8 14c1.5-1 3-1.5 4-1.5" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Calm</h3>
        <div class="benefit-dose">400mg Reishi</div>
        <p>The adaptogenic "chill mushroom." Helps your body buffer stress and find balance — sharp and steady, not wired.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Hydration -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon-wrap" style="background:#E3F5F7;">
          <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 3C12 3 5 10.5 5 15a7 7 0 0 0 14 0c0-4.5-7-12-7-12z" fill="#50B2BD"/>
            <path d="M9 16a3 3 0 0 0 3 2" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Hydration</h3>
        <div class="benefit-dose">Ocean Minerals</div>
        <p>Deep ocean-derived magnesium and calcium for cellular hydration and electrolyte balance. Rehydrate, not just hydrate.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

